                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000afedb561-4c44-4196-b1dc-56aa56d88925" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({E}_{k}=\left(m-{m}_{0}\right){c}^{2}⇒{m}_{0}{c}^{2}=m{c}^{2}-{m}_{0}{c}^{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001afedb561-4c44-4196-b1dc-56aa56d88925"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000afedb561-4c44-4196-b1dc-56aa56d88925 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001afedb561-4c44-4196-b1dc-56aa56d88925 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000004a48849d-ba25-4153-b535-eaf6764e3718" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴m=2{m}_{0};\ v=\sqrt{1-{\left(\frac{{m}_{0}}{m}\right)}^{2}}\times c\ =\sqrt{1-\frac{1}{4}}\times c=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}c\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014a48849d-ba25-4153-b535-eaf6764e3718"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000004a48849d-ba25-4153-b535-eaf6764e3718 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000014a48849d-ba25-4153-b535-eaf6764e3718 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000abdbb7ac-8be0-4100-8899-bea612146f39" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(p=mv=2{m}_{0}\times \frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}c=\sqrt{3}{m}_{0}c\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001abdbb7ac-8be0-4100-8899-bea612146f39"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000abdbb7ac-8be0-4100-8899-bea612146f39 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001abdbb7ac-8be0-4100-8899-