                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000001d1f987-d2e4-4ec5-8300-8f2d63214e02" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000101d1f987-d2e4-4ec5-8300-8f2d63214e02"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 1.083333in;height: 0.5578839in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000001d1f987-d2e4-4ec5-8300-8f2d63214e02 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000101d1f987-d2e4-4ec5-8300-8f2d63214e02 {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000005eb4de1a-99df-4e78-a032-21746348db91" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{P}{BC}=\frac{3P}{AC}=\frac{4P}{AB}….(i)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000015eb4de1a-99df-4e78-a032-21746348db91"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005eb4de1a-99df-4e78-a032-21746348db91 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000015eb4de1a-99df-4e78-a032-21746348db91 {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000049e25594-6eb3-43c0-ba7d-f17168ed3c1e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000149e25594-6eb3-43c0-ba7d-f17168ed3c1e">Avevi</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000149e25594-6eb3-43c0-ba7d-f17168ed3c1e">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{P}{AD}=\frac{3P}{BD}=\frac{4P}{AB}….\ (ii)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000149e25594-6eb3-43c0-ba7d-f17168ed3c1e"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000049e25594-6eb3-43c0-ba7d-f17168ed3c1e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000149e25594-6eb3-43c0-ba7d-f17168ed3c1e {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color