                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000000b9d4e2c-b491-451c-9f0a-2158cc4ac263" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(R=2Acos\frac{α}{2}⇒2P=2\sqrt{2}Pcos\ {\frac{α}{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010b9d4e2c-b491-451c-9f0a-2158cc4ac263"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000b9d4e2c-b491-451c-9f0a-2158cc4ac263 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010b9d4e2c-b491-451c-9f0a-2158cc4ac263 {font-family: ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000047319ec2-f084-496b-9d3c-f1450f71b102" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒cos\frac{α}{2}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}∴\ \frac{α}{2}=45^{\circ} \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000147319ec2-f084-496b-9d3c-f1450f71b102"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000047319ec2-f084-496b-9d3c-f1450f71b102 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000147319ec2-f084-496b-9d3c-f1450f71b102 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
